Welcome to the official [Helm](https://helm.sh/) chart repository for [GraphViews](https://help.poolparty.biz/pp2024r1/en/user-guide-for-knowledge-engineers/add-on/poolparty-graphviews.html)!
This Helm chart makes it easy to deploy and manage GraphViews on your [Kubernetes](https://kubernetes.io/) cluster.

# About GraphViews

PoolParty GraphViews makes it easy to gain an overview of knowledge graphs. It allows users to explore, visualize, and
interact with linked data to uncover connections, identify trends, exceptions, and patterns, and gain new insights. Graph
visualizations support informed decision-making and can be downloaded or shared to integrate seamlessly into analystsâ€™ workflows.

